Revision history for WebService-Flattr

0.55 2013-03-24
  - Support Flattr's "X-RateLimit-Reset" HTTP header

0.54 2012-07-23
  - Add a rate_limit() query method

0.53 2012-03-05
  - Add a thing_flattrs() query method
  - Fix get_things() to deal with Flattr's incompatible change
  - Fix a module's name in its documentation

0.52 2012-02-05
  - Add things_owned_by() and get_things() query methods
  - Minor documentation improvements

0.51 2012-02-01
  - Future proof search queries
  - Set the LWP::UserAgent name
  - Minor documentation fix

0.50 2012-01-22
  - Initial release to CPAN
